Package ca.cgjennings.spelling.dict

Interface FrequencyAnalyzer.CorpusProcessor

All Known Implementing Classes:
FrequencyAnalyzer.AbstractCorpusProcessor, FrequencyAnalyzer.ColumnDataFileProcessor, FrequencyAnalyzer.ProseProcessor
Enclosing class:
FrequencyAnalyzer
public static interface FrequencyAnalyzer.CorpusProcessor
A corpus processor tokenizes a corpus file into words and informs a FrequencyAnalyzer of the words that it encounters. Different concrete implementations are used to process different source file formats.
